    dc:description "Fig. 1. Ophichthus pratasensis, new species, holotype, fresh, NMMB-P35993, 585 mm TL. A, lateral view; B, lateral view of right side of head; C, posterior portion of tail, left side, anterior to left, preserved. Not to scale." ;
