    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174547>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Drawings of (A) head pores and (B) teeth on upper jaw (left) and lower jaw (right). Knob between nostrils is indicated by arrow. Missing teeth are represented by dotted lines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7174547/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

